article_id:3033,category_name:News,title_name:Gala Dragalia Is Now Live!,image_path:,message:<div>Gala Dragalia started on <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1664431200"></span>!</div><div><br></div><div>■What Are Gala Dragalia and Gala Dragalia Remix?</div><div>The initial appearance rate for 5★ adventurers and dragons is boosted to 6%, which is up from the standard 4%! If you get a 5★ summon or 5★ featured summon, the appearance rate will return to the initial 6%.</div><div><br></div><div>▼Featured adventurers:</div><div>5★ Gala Notte (wind/dagger)</div><div>5★ Gala Ranzal (wind/sword)</div><div><br></div><div>▼Featured dragon:</div><div>5★ Gala Reborn Zephyr (wind)</div><div><br></div><div>Gala Dragalia appearance rates:</div><div>5★ total: 6.00%</div><div>5★ featured total: 1.80% (Adventurers: 1.00%, Dragons: 0.80%)</div><div>5★ standard total: 4.20% (Adventurers: 2.00%, Dragons: 2.20%)</div><div>4★ standard total: 16.00% (Adventurers: 8.55%, Dragons: 7.45%)</div><div>3★ standard total: 78.00% (Adventurers: 47.00%, Dragons: 31.00%)</div><div><br></div><div>Gala Dragalia event duration:</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1664431200"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1664863199"></span></div><div><br></div><div>Get a closer look at the featured adventurers and dragon below.</div><div><br></div><div>Featured adventurers:</div><div>
